---
import DocsLayout from "../layouts/DocsLayout.astro";
---

<DocsLayout title="Changelog — hemingway-ai" heading="Changelog">
  <h2>v0.1.0</h2>

  <h3>Added</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>CLI server with AI-powered copy generation via Anthropic Claude</li>
    <li>Browser overlay with automatic text discovery and selection</li>
    <li>React component wrapper (<code>hemingway-ai/react</code>)</li>
    <li>Source file write-back with heuristic text matching</li>
    <li>Multi-element selection for cohesive rewrites (2–5 elements)</li>
    <li>Inline editing with double-click</li>
    <li>Style preference learning from user picks</li>
    <li>Copy job classification (headline, CTA, body copy, etc.)</li>
    <li>Section role detection (hero, features, pricing, etc.)</li>
    <li>Page brief generation for full-page context</li>
    <li>Style guide and copy bible configuration</li>
    <li>Built-in demo page at /demo</li>
    <li>Configurable keyboard shortcut, accent color, and model</li>
  </ul>
</DocsLayout>
